name: LEAVE ME ALONE
description:
(1/5) Social Norms and Misjudgments

All Tezos given will be donated to the mentalhealthfoundation.org to help those who need it more than myself. This is to help spread the message of importance of mental health and to give back to this amazing community in any way that I can. 

This collection will be a series of 5 images, all listed at 5 tez. I will share proof of our donations once either all editions have been claimed, or after the next two weeks of the mint being public. 

Thank you to everyone who participates in this collection to help the people in our community who may need it.
